<form (submit)="onlogin(loginform)" #loginform="ngForm">
    <input type="text"
    ngModel name="enteredusername"
    placeholder="username"
    required
    minlength="1"
    pattern="^[\w-\.]+@([\w-]+\.)+[\w-]{2,4}$"
    #enteredusername ="ngModel"/>
    <input type="password"
    ngModel name="enteredpassword"
    placeholder="password"
    required
    minlength="1"
    pattern="^([a_zA-Z0-9@*#]{8,15})$"
    #enteredusername ="ngModel"/>

<button type="submit" >{{}option}</button>
</form>
